#include <cstdio>

int main(){
	int t, xl1, xl2, xr1, xr2, yl1, yl2, yr1, yr2, xl, xr, yl, yr;
	
	scanf("%d", &t);
	while (t--){
		scanf("%d%d%d%d", &xl1, &yl1, &xr1, &yr1);
		scanf("%d%d%d%d", &xl2, &yl2, &xr2, &yr2);
		
		xl = xl1 > xl2 ? xl1 : xl2;
		yl = yl1 > yl2 ? yl1 : yl2;
		xr = xr1 < xr2 ? xr1 : xr2;
		yr = yr1 < yr2 ? yr1 : yr2;
		if (xl < xr && yl < yr)
			printf("%d %d %d %d\n", xl, yl, xr, yr);
		else
			printf("No Overlap\n");
	}
	
	return 0;
}
